modules.description: This module parses and processes TextMate grammars for syntax highlighting, supporting loading grammars from PLIST or JSON data structures and managing collections of grammars by name, scope, or file type. It provides functions to tokenize source code lines using a specified grammar, returning token scopes and positions, and maintains parser state across lines. Concrete use cases include integrating TextMate syntax definitions into editors or tools that require incremental tokenization of source code.
